Message that appears when there is no templatedata for a MediaWiki template chosen in Step 1: Metadata detection. Parameters:
* $1 - the name of the chosen template
* $2 - a link to the MediaWiki templatedata help page for adding a templatedata block to a template
Link text used is {{msg-mw|Gwtoolset-templatedata-link-text}}
* $3 - a link to the commons help page for adding templatedata to a template's templatebox
Link text used is {{msg-mw|Gwtoolset-templatebox-link-text}}
